MBOMBELA &#8211; R800 000&#8217;s worth of alcohol was recovered at noon on Saturday after a suspect was busted by CSG Hi-Tech Nelspruit.The alcohol had been stolen from the SPAR Lowveld Distribution Centre in Vintonia.&nbsp;&#8220;The operation was planned last week in which we were able to arrest the suspect and recover the stolen goods,&#8221; said Callum MacPherson, Hi-Tech&#8217;s response manager.Lowvelder will publish more information as soon as it becomes available.&nbsp;